# Image Assets Directory

This directory contains image assets for the Hindu Hate Index platform.

## Structure

- `/logos` - Platform logos and branding
- `/icons` - Custom icons and graphics
- `/illustrations` - Illustrations and decorative images
- `/photos` - Photographs and real images
- `/backgrounds` - Background images and patterns

## Guidelines

- Use WebP format for better compression when possible
- Provide multiple sizes for responsive images
- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., `hero-background-1920x1080.webp`)
- Optimize images before adding them to the repository
